Category:Unidentified Sith of the One Sith

nodes.text: Three Zabrak Sith of the One Sith were present at the Battle of Vendaxa in 137 ABY. One black-eyed and haired male attempted to assault a dazed Cade Skywalker when the Sith was killed by Marasiah Fel, but not before he wounded Fel in the process.
